    <item>
      <title>马杜罗请求友好委内瑞拉法庭核实其选举胜利</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-31/maduro-asks-friendly-venezuela-court-to-verify-his-election-win</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尽管反对派声称有证据证明总统尼古拉斯·马杜罗窃取了选票，但总统尼古拉斯·马杜罗仍要求委内瑞拉最高法院审计周日总统选举的结果，以证明其自我宣布的胜利合法化。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-31/maduro-asks-friendly-venezuela-court-to-verify-his-election-win</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 18:36:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普在与黑人记者的活动中质疑卡马拉·哈里斯的种族</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-31/trump-questions-harris-race-at-event-with-black-journalists</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普在与黑人记者举行的激烈圆桌会议上质疑副总统卡玛拉·哈里斯的种族身份。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-31/trump-questions-harris-race-at-event-with-black-journalists</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 18:26:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>商业大亨敦促哈里斯罢免拜登的联邦贸易委员会主席莉娜·汗</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-31/business-moguls-urge-harris-to-dump-biden-s-ftc-chair-lina-khan</link>
      <description><![CDATA[莉娜·汗 (Lina Khan) 从未受到亿万富翁的欢迎，但现在两位著名的商业巨头希望副总统卡玛拉·哈里斯 (Kamala Harris) 在入主白宫后放弃联邦贸易委员会主席的职务。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-31/business-moguls-urge-harris-to-dump-biden-s-ftc-chair-lina-khan</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 18:11:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>尽管可能征收关税，中国比亚迪仍寻求进入加拿大电动汽车市场</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-31/china-s-byd-seeks-entry-to-canada-ev-market-despite-likely-tariffs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[正当加拿大总理贾斯汀·特鲁多的政府努力限制从亚洲强国进口汽车之际，中国电动汽车制造商比亚迪股份有限公司正寻求进入加拿大市场。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-31/china-s-byd-seeks-entry-to-canada-ev-market-despite-likely-tariffs</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 17:52:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>尼日利亚加强首都安保以应对全国抗议活动</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-31/nigeria-tightens-security-in-capital-before-national-protests</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尼日利亚全国范围内爆发抗议活动，抗议食品和燃料价格过高，加剧了该国的生活成本危机。在抗议活动爆发前夕，尼日利亚在首都阿布贾部署了安全部队。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-31/nigeria-tightens-security-in-capital-before-national-protests</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 16:56:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马杜罗冒着阿根廷大使馆对峙引发地区分裂的风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-31/venezuela-s-maduro-risks-regional-retribution-in-argentina-embassy-standoff</link>
      <description><![CDATA[委内瑞拉反对派领导人的助手躲藏在阿根廷驻加拉加斯大使馆，那里正在酝酿一场僵局，这可能会进一步孤立独裁总统尼古拉斯·马杜罗。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-31/venezuela-s-maduro-risks-regional-retribution-in-argentina-embassy-standoff</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 16:15:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>联合国称以色列任意监禁和折磨巴勒斯坦人</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-31/un-says-israel-is-arbitrarily-jailing-torturing-palestinians</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据联合国新报告称，自与哈马斯开战以来，以色列任意拘留了数千名巴勒斯坦人，许多人遭受了“恶劣条件”，包括酷刑和性暴力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-31/un-says-israel-is-arbitrarily-jailing-torturing-palestinians</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 15:43:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>乌克兰经过漫长等待终于接收首批 F-16 战斗机</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-31/ukraine-gets-first-delivery-of-f-16-fighter-jets-after-long-wait</link>
      <description><![CDATA[北约盟国交付的首批 F-16 战斗机已抵达乌克兰，这一期待已久的举措可能增强这个饱受战争蹂躏的国家抵御俄罗斯袭击的能力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-31/ukraine-gets-first-delivery-of-f-16-fighter-jets-after-long-wait</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 15:05:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>尽管暗杀事件受挫，美国仍推动加沙停火谈判</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-31/biden-team-still-pushing-gaza-cease-fire-after-israel-s-strikes</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据熟悉拜登政府想法的人士透露，美国官员仍在推动加沙停火，但承认在以色列疑似袭击导致哈马斯高级领导人在德黑兰死亡后，停火比以往任何时候都更加困难。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-31/biden-team-still-pushing-gaza-cease-fire-after-israel-s-strikes</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 14:17:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>袭击德黑兰和贝鲁特的以色列敌人导致紧张局势加剧</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-31/regional-risks-rise-as-israel-says-two-enemies-killed-abroad</link>
      <description><![CDATA[哈马斯和真主党高层领导人在国外遭到袭击仅几个小时，此举引发了地区冲突的可能性，以色列表明了其愿意冒险进行报复。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-31/regional-risks-rise-as-israel-says-two-enemies-killed-abroad</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 08:41:06 GMT</pubDate>
